<sect1 id="less" xreflabel="less-&less-version;">
  <?dbhtml filename="less.html"?>

  <title>less-&less-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      less is a terminal pager program used to view the contents of a text file
      one screen at a time.
    </para>

