  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Prepare the package for compilation:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Compile the package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>porg -lD "make -j1 install"</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
    <title>Configuration</title>

    <para>
      Default BusyBox man pager is <command>more</command>. You can improve it
      by setting the <envar>MANPAGER</envar> variable to "less -R".
    </para>

